<br>
/pet sit down<br>
Find Darkweed Snake<br>
Flame Bolt it for 41 to pull<br>
Run behind Kantik<br>
/pet attack %T<br>
Shock of Blades<br>
Shock of Blades<br>
Let pet finish off the mob<br>
<br>
Rinse, Meditate to full, Repeat. <br>
<br>
Works well on Lions and Lionesses as well as Giant Spiders. Yes, I'm also taking down Yellow's already at my level with no difficulty at all. Still a newbie to being a Mage but learning everyday.<br>
